{"tid":440324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"柒黎講 我都算極致","createTime":"2017-10-18T15:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T05:20:00.000Z","uid":149290,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"de321863e559ed0debc420b34f9964c5bcbab6ba","tid":440324,"uid":149290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"話說之前朝早搭火車返工<br />\n好唔容易逼到上車<br />\n係佢 嗶嗶嗶嗶 之際<br />\n有人推左我一野 幾乎比車門夾到個頭<br />\n我頭一縮....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/234529_cf9a9cb33a1db0b1458d11581172bbca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F234529_cf9a9cb33a1db0b1458d11581172bbca.jpg&h=125ac761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌佢老母 夾住左我副眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成車人笑到仆街望住<br />\n我都算 諗住忍到下個站執返即刻落車扮無野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母 佢開對面度門<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0802fb8bdd4d5f06fee58782df62ccea63b9a21","tid":440324,"uid":46158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa19632f8b9b4b9d7bdc013b4006f0fed82c0fad","tid":440324,"uid":151833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:41:25.000Z","msg":"然後呢"},{"pid":"d1563de1c30d20dc1464e410a6adb1501f1192ef","tid":440324,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8049844aa7c2a7f88bca0aa751979f17b63a401","tid":440324,"uid":58502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg